snippet.title: DC UNIVERSE ONLINE Lightning Strikes DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
Classic Game Room's CGRtrailers presents the "Lightning Strikes" DLC trailer for DC UNIVERSE ONLINE. DC Universe Online is from WB Games, DC Comics and Sony Online Entertainment. As you can probably tell, this DLC deals with the Scarlet Speedster - The Flash! The costumes not only give it way, but so does the famous Flash Museum from Central City in the DC Comics universe. The DLC is downloadable now! Enjoy!

Check out more video game trailers from Classic Game Room's CGRtrailers at http://www.youtube.com/CGRtrailers

Get more Classic Game Room on Facebook at http://www.facebook.com/ClassicGameRoom
